	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just to make sure there is no confusion...Grizzly Bear Skins ARE NOT used to make 10 slot backpacks.  Those are HQ Bear Pelts.  <br><br>1 spiderling silk + 1 spiderling silk = silk thread<br><br>silk thread + silk thread + silk thread = silk cord<br><br>Grizzly Bear Skin + Silk Cord = Bearskin Potion Bag<br><br>The potion bag is a 10 slot for SMALL items and can be used by shamans to make potions.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
